29218&amp;snA=35&amp;tnum=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D29218%26snA%3D35%26tnum%3D4&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=4bb5592e\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29218&amp;snA=35&amp;tnum=4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://games.gaym.jp/iPhone/bukiyosaraba/wiki/?%EF%BC%BB%E7%BE%8E%E3%81%97%E3%81%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%BF%83%E6%A3%92%EF%BC%BD%E3%82%B5%E3%83%A4%E3%82%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgames.gaym.jp%2FiPhone%2Fbukiyosaraba%2Fwiki%2F%3F%25EF%25BC%25BB%25E7%25BE%258E%25E3%2581%2597%25E3%2581%258D%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%25A3%2592%25EF%25BC%25BD%25E3%2582%25B5%25E3%2583%25A4%25E3%2582%25AB&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=423f4681\" target=\"_blank\">http://games.gaym.jp/iPhone/bukiyosaraba/wiki/?%EF%BC%BB%E7%BE%8E%E3%81%97%E3%81%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%BF%83%E6%A3%92%EF%BC%BD%E3%82%B5%E3%83%A4%E3%82%AB</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>新手導航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n玩法好簡單 見識郁嘅野就斬9佢就冇死既<br />\n斬唔死?斬多幾下啦<br />\n分普攻重擊同大技<br />\n重擊有CD<br />\n普攻會儲氣 100%就可以開大技<br />\n開緊大技會有無敵<br />\n4類怪<br />\n灰色兵<br />\n有顏色既兵-&gt;有屬性 剋屬會斬得好快<br />\n小boss 多D血,會開技,用碌避佢攻擊再斬9佢就得,硬殺都得<br />\n大boss 教學最尾果隻 條血會show係畫面上方 幾個大都未必殺到 都係碌下再斬下 大鎚好似可以硬殺<br />\n建築物唔一定要打爆<br />\n每一關都有3粒星,達成條件有一石拎(每粒星)<br />\n普遍係<br />\n1.唔死人<br />\n2.打哂D箱/50殺<br />\n3.3分鐘內過關<br />\n打完1/2章有50石送<br />\n石最好留/抽武搏連專<br />\n唔啱屬可以用住好友D5星先<br />\n28日會送5星人<br />\nBy 不借得太多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>首抽推薦:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n如果想舒服d最好刷到起碼兩隻五星先起手<br />\n至少要有一隻雙刀/劍<br />\n拳鎚會辛苦少少<br />\n個人排單隻首抽順序會係<br />\n雷雙&gt;木劍=水雙=雷拳=火鎚=水拳&gt;木鎚=巫女(唔計樣)<br />\n首抽相對易刷<br />\n真正難刷嘅係專屬武器<br />\n五星專武比四星武多一個被動<br />\n而個被動就係某屬性傷害提高<br />\n而武器種類唔可以亂裝<br />\n結果就係只有一隻五星可以食到個效果(暫時)<br />\n而個出五星武嘅機率係2% 八把<br />\n所以好難中專屬武器<br />\nBy不借得太多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>遠征教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n解放條件：完成主線第一至第三章normal<br />\n玩法：<br />\n只能揀30隻角色打n關<br />\n每關能揀3隻出場<br />\n血量同sp量都會繼承落下一關<br />\n只能靠每關內隨機出現既寶箱回血<br />\n某啲關卡有過關獎勵<br />\n有金箱同銀箱<br />\n會隨機出不同獎品<br />\n每日可以再新開始一次遠征<br />\n7日打唔晒要重新打過<br />\n現時關卡數量不明<br />\n建議：<br />\n帶回血角色eg:雷拳，4星水雙<br />\n被扣血或有損傷可以退場或再挑戰<br />\n盡量帶剋屬角<br />\nBy 碎穴無聲<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<strong>連登公會list</strong><br />\nLihkg ID:319955087<br />\nLIHKG2 ID:718969330<br />\n連登 ID:589284160<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">申請入會時記得留名講聲自己ID同對下個公會ID，以免入錯公會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>各位課主課金時記得轉日本時區，否則入game會system error</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"ce83d6346d69d2f40176f7b6324969e4787f7ee4","tid":207653,"uid":24617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"仲要轉番日本iTunes&nbsp;Ac先入到去課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6d9f017faeb8c49f26fadd9935a02fee156491","tid":207653,"uid":39682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"新手留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44df751f07efc1027adf1bc63c81c0d42e64496a","tid":207653,"uid":72343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打有冇興趣入公會"},{"pid":"2b6389413a6804d9851cf3184b898a2022100a9b","tid":207653,"uid":106555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"刷免費雙劍武淨最難果關刷左最少200場以上<br />\n，very hard又300場以上，一把都無跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smi